{
  "stem": "15694.9",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I have stepped out a life out of the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It came later to me that I was stood in the place probably of the biggest death cry ever heard, where so many thousands in crammed condition were put in.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the big trains arrived, not our small group, where they have pushed in people to capacity, and in order for production to go faster and better, thrown the little ones on top of them.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I stood at that spot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But these thoughts only came later to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we were always together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we had-- it was at a later stage when we parted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we'd come to that later-- always together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, it was part of our survival, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, we stood in front of the designated barracks for hours in hot sunshine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were alive, but at the same time after a while, you also get tired.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you get hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Eventually, a kapo came, which the so-called [NON-ENGLISH] in this particular camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was dressed in the same pajama pants, striped suits, but his trousers were ironed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His jacket was made to measure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And his hat even had a sort of, like a point, as if to imitate the military hat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it had no shield, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he told us that we shouldn't expect anything for three days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Newcomers don't get anything for three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he wants to impress us, and he did duly by telling us that to make room for us, the night before they killed 4,000 gypsies.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, we were duly impressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We also found out that these gypsies, before they were killed, were given the night before a good meal, sausages, and what have you.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
